The '''Army Weapons Research Department''' were the research branch of the [[Grand Army of the Republic/Legends|Grand Army of the Republic]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]]. Some members of this branch set up a base on the rogue [[Planet/Legends|planetoid]] [[Tembora]], known as [[Tembora Research Station]]. It is here that they tried to develop the [[KLR series combat droid|KLR-series combat droid]]. Unfortunately, the software programming in the [[Droid/Legends|droids]] was unstable, allowing them to overwrite their failsafes. [[KLR-B1]] injured two technicians and killed a third before they decided to shut down the droids and start the programming from scratch. Somehow KLR-B1 was not shut down, and instead went on a psychopathic rampage, killing all members of the research station and any crewmembers of ships which crashed on the planetoid.

